_sText:
The walls are breakable, and you'll find the way they break to be very fun.
There are working escalators.
Note: I was not trying to replicate the matrix lobby scene, because its too boring of a level. So I remixed it to fit the type of fast FY gameplay that I was working towards.
P.S. It was a quick make, and is meant to be fun! If you can think of ways I can make it look nicer, tell me!
P.S.S. find custom maps by myself and clan members at our server 4.79.145.222:27015 add us to your favorites :D
